#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.kblocks.appdata.xml:9
msgid "KBlocks"
msgstr "KBlocks"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.kblocks.appdata.xml:10
msgid "Falling Blocks Game"
msgstr "Erortzen diren blokeen jokoa"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kblocks.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"KBlocks is the classic falling blocks game. The idea is to stack the falling "
"blocks to create horizontal lines without any gaps. When a line is completed "
"it is removed, and more space is available in the play area. When there is "
"not enough space for blocks to fall, the game is over."
msgstr ""
"KBlocks erortzen diren blokeen joko klasikoa da. Erortzen diren blokeak "
"pilatzea da helburua, arrakalarik gabeko lerro horizontalak sortzeko. Lerro "
"bat osatu denean, kendu egiten da, eta jokalekuan leku gehiago dago. Blokeak "
"erortzeko lekurik gelditzen ez denean, jokoa amaitu da."
